// Onboarding Topic Detail
// Detailed view of a single onboarding topic. Displays content in tabbed sections
// (Overview, Technical, Files, Related, Diagrams) with a related topics sidebar.
// In onboarding mode, also shows progress buttons and a personal notes section.

FUNCTION parseRelatedLinks(content) -> string[] [private]
  Extract topic slugs from markdown links in the format [label](../slug) and **bold-slug** patterns.

---

FUNCTION TopicDetail()                                                  EXPORT
  CALLS: getTopic (onboarding-api), getDiagrams (onboarding-api), getProgress (onboarding-api), getNotes (onboarding-api), markProgress (onboarding-api), deleteProgress (onboarding-api), addNote (onboarding-api), deleteNote (onboarding-api)
  Read name from URL params. Read project, mode, currentUser from OnboardingContext.
  On mount: fetch topic content and parse related links from the 'related' content field.
  Fetch diagrams in parallel.
  In onboarding mode: also fetch user progress and notes for this topic.

  handleMark(status): call onboardingApi.markProgress and update local progress state.
  handleUndo: call onboardingApi.deleteProgress and clear local progress.
  handleAddNote: call onboardingApi.addNote, prepend to notes list.
  handleDeleteNote: call onboardingApi.deleteNote, remove from notes list.

  Render:
    - Topic title and slug header.
    - (Onboarding mode) Progress buttons: "Mark Done" / "Skip" or current status with undo.
    - Tabbed content: Overview, Technical, Files, Related rendered as Markdown; Diagrams via DiagramsTab.
    - (Onboarding mode) Notes section with add-note form and list of existing notes.
    - Related topics sidebar (parsed from content) linking to other topic detail pages.
